{{> heading title="RP E-Portfolio - Project Supervisor Update: Supervisor Reactivation"}}

        <main style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7;">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 500;">Dear {{studentName}},</p>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 32px; color: #374151;">
This is to inform you that {{supervisorName}}, who was a supervisor on some of your projects has had their account reactivated in the RP E-Portfolio system.
            </p>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">What this means for the project:</h3>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin: 0;">
                    <li style="position: relative; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #374151;">
                        <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #6b7280; font-weight: bold;">•</span>
                        Their name will now appear in all your projects' displays if they are still assigned to him/her
                    </li>
                    <li style="position: relative; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #374151;">
                        <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #6b7280; font-weight: bold;">•</span>
                        Their past contributions remain attributed in all projects' history if they are still assigned to him/her
                    </li>
                    <li style="position: relative; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #374151;">
                        <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: #6b7280; font-weight: bold;">•</span>
                        Project Owner Name continues to manage the projects
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 32px; color: #374151;">
                        If you have any questions about this change, please contact <span style="font-weight: bold;">{{collegeAdminContact}}</span>
            </p>

        {{> footer2 college=college}}

        </main>
    </div>
</body>
